channel.title: [PI] Need help with adding in donator rank
channel.description: Is there any tutorial specifically written for PI on how to add in donator rank. I saw a few out there, but people seem to say they aren't that good or it doesn't look like it was designed for PI. If possible, both server and client side would be appreciated. Adding the status and the icon.
